    28→/* The Term interface correspond to AST's that when output as concrete syntax by toString() can be used as terms 
    29→ * in an iterative binary expression without enclosing parentheses. We enclose all binary expressions in parentheses
    30→ * so we do not presume either left or right associativity for infix binary operators. */
    31→/** Term ::= Constant | PrimFun | Variable | UnOpApp |  App */
    32→interface Term extends AST {}
